Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DCMain,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Conan Episode 764 "Conan \Nand Heiji's Code of Love (Part 2)"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,DCMain,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:04.65,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The Detective Boys, Haibara, and I
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.65,0:00:09.73,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,ran into a suspicious man being pursued\Nin the rain by men who seemed like cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.60,0:00:15.43,DCMain,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Damn kids! Watch where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:16.70,DCMain,COP,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.21,0:00:21.08,DCMain,COP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:28.87,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The man was apparently a drug dealer,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:34.52,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,and I deduced the time and location of his \Ndrug deal from the notebook he dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:40.03,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the code E22 \Nis associated with "ma,"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:45.79,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Y21 with "tsuki," and \N"G11" with "Nihon."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.79,0:00:52.28,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I realized immediately that they \Nwere subway and station numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:53.36,DCMain,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:58.31,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The third number in E22 was circled,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.31,0:01:01.82,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,and the third character\Nin Azabu Juban is "ju."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.82,0:01:05.43,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,If you read the code up to the \Nfifth line following that rule,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:08.36,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,E22 is "ju."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.36,0:01:11.83,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,C10 is the Chiyoda Line's Nijubashimae.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.83,0:01:13.80,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The first letter is circled, so it's "ni."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.43,0:01:18.50,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Y21 is the Yurakucho Line's \NTsukishima, so it's "tsuki."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.50,0:01:22.85,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}M09 is the Marunouchi Line's Shinjuku \NSanchome, so it's "san."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:26.49,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}G11 is the Ginza Line's \NNihonbashi, so it's "hi."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.49,0:01:30.02,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If you read them in order, \Nyou get December 3rd.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:35.57,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,However, the code included \Nmysteries I couldn't decipher,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.17,0:01:39.87,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,and I ended up working with \NHattori Heiji over the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:43.40,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:48.67,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,It's a code using line and\Nstation numbers, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:50.71,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:55.13,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, some of the codes \Nare aligned to the left,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:57.60,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,and some of them are aligned to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.60,0:01:58.47,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.92,0:02:01.46,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.46,0:02:06.47,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe one side indicates Tokyo stations \Nand the other indicates Osaka stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.47,0:02:09.90,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, it would natural to assume
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:13.36,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,the western city of Osaka is the left and \Nthe eastern city of Tokyo is the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:15.63,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! The escalator!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:16.24,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:22.10,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,On an escalator, in Osaka we stand to\Nthe right and leave the left side open,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.11,0:02:24.09,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,but it's the other way \Naround in Tokyo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.09,0:02:28.21,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The stations aligned to the \Nright are Osaka stations,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:31.75,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,and the ones aligned to the \Nleft are Tokyo stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:33.77,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hattori.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:36.72,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Is there an Ebisu bridge over there, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.48,0:02:40.38,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:44.00,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,There's one in Osaka, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.32,0:02:47.12,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The characters are different,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.04,0:02:52.56,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,but there's a bridge called Ebisubashi \Nwhere we meet all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:55.52,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:57.23,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:02:59.52,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,You can't hear him anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.52,0:03:01.53,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:05.83,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he tried to catch the dealer's \Ntrading partner, and instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:08.52,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,He's pretty hot-blooded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:10.05,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:11.04,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hattori!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:13.67,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Hattori!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:14.85,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:16.38,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,There are three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:21.18,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I just took a look around Ebisubashi,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:27.18,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,but there are three people wearing or holding\Nwhite roses while waiting for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:33.31,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,But there are only five minutes to noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:34.52,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:39.23,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we'll have to narrow down \Nhis trading partner to one before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:42.32,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:47.04,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The hidden lines on the palm are the fuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:48.95,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The deduction catches fire \Non the line to the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:50.95,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,A collaborative deduction \Nusing smart phone images.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:53.04,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,How will Hattori respond when he sees Kazuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:56.38,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Always determining the one truth with the \Nbody of a child and the mind of an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:58.55,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,his name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:44.99,DCEpTitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)}Conan and Heiji's Code of Love\N(Part 2)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:43.70,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Conan and Heiji's Code of Love, Part 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:48.99,Ebisubashi,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Ebisubashi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:48.99,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:51.96,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What do the three people look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:54.52,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,It's two guys and one girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:57.75,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to video chat you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:06:03.35,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,If the dealer shows up, you'll recognize him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:05.51,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Keep this phone line open.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:07.76,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Send the images to my phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:08.69,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:13.51,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:14.73,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:16.09,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,We can see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:17.37,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,The image is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:19.14,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Who are the three people?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.63,0:06:21.90,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Right. The first one
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:25.90,DCMain,HIEJI,0000,0000,0000,,is this scary looking old dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:29.85,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,He looks like bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:34.07,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,He's suspicious. He keeps checking the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.07,0:06:36.66,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,He has an expensive watch, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:39.03,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of checking...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:39.79,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Look, he did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:44.00,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,He took something out of his coat's \Ninside pocket and is looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:45.93,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be a cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:48.73,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,He's waving it in front of his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:50.55,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's some kind of signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:53.85,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he hasn't gotten much sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:56.13,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,He keeps yawning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:07:01.43,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see a white rose anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:02.23,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Is it in his right hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:03.75,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:06.61,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,In his right hand, he's carefully holding...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:09.88,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,...a bouquet of white roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:15.06,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this the bad guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:16.60,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:17.95,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:19.75,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Who are the other two?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:26.14,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The next one is this lady wearing \Na white rose in her hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:31.17,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Her hair is so cute and wavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:32.66,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Is she a model?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:34.67,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Is she meeting someone for a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.67,0:07:35.80,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,She's suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:36.69,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:38.97,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,Look closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:41.39,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,The bag she's holding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:44.94,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,That's the newest Fusae brand model.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:49.27,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,It's unbelievably expensive, but \Nshe stuck a rose corsage on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:51.95,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,That's not on sale in Japan yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:54.20,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where she got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:56.12,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,That's what drew your attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:58.99,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? She's looking at her shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:01.34,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Did she step on something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:03.37,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,She's crouching.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:07.79,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,She put something inside her shoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:11.18,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,This lady's suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:12.77,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:13.93,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:22.59,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The third person is this gaudy guy \Nwearing a white rose on his chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:26.44,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, he's talking to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:28.92,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:31.89,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,For a while now he's been \Ntalking to some girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:37.14,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kazuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:41.16,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:43.77,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hattori.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:47.91,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,That girl looks like Kazuha-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.91,0:08:48.67,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:50.80,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kazuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:54.93,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot's getting hit on by\Nsome good-for-nothing guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:58.93,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,This guy must be innocent, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:03.26,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,No one's stupid enough to \Nhit on a girl before a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.26,0:09:07.51,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Could he be one of Kazuha's \Nlaw enforcement acquaintances?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:09.56,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, look closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:13.84,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,He's got bleached hair, a pierced \Nnose, and a tattoo on his neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:16.07,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Cops don't look like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:18.04,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:20.70,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,There are less than two minutes to noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:23.26,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time, Hattori.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:25.01,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:27.52,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,If it's not the flashy guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:30.71,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,it's got to be either the \Nold dude or the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:48.66,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hattori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:50.02,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Can I tell you what I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:52.25,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:54.29,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hattori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:56.03,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:01.12,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Shit. I can't focus...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:04.28,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:06.04,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hattori!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:09.04,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening, Hattori?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:10.65,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:12.54,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Quit shouting at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:15.99,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to tell me what you \Nthink, spit it out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:17.72,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:19.05,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,First, the old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:23.60,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The scary looking man with \Nthe bouquet of white roses
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:25.72,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,isn't the dealer's trading partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:27.39,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:30.73,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,He certainly has the most \Nsuspicious face of the bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:34.48,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,He was taking something out of his coat, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:37.99,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like he was sending \Nsome kind of weird signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:39.20,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:42.70,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,He was using a hand mirror \Nto check his bangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:46.11,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It just looked weird because he was \Nusing his fingers to fix his bangs
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:48.50,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,while holding the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:50.75,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Why was he yawning, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.97,0:10:55.81,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,He was checking to see if his breath smelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:10:59.48,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,He was hiding the bouquet of roses \Nbehind his back while he waited
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:03.27,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,because he wants to surprise \Nwhoever he's meeting with a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:04.26,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:08.13,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,If the white rose is a sign,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:11.81,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,he would be holding it in a more obvious way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:14.77,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,This old guy probably
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.75,0:11:20.90,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,is waiting for his date.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.11,DCMain,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}They're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:20.90,DCMain,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Are they for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.25,0:11:22.91,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:24.26,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:26.63,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Conan's master!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.63,0:11:27.97,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:29.91,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Most of that was my deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:34.79,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,What about the woman wearing \Na white rose on her head?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:38.05,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Her shoes seemed to bother her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:41.23,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,She crouched and put something in her shoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.23,0:11:43.55,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been a small \Nweapon or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:44.80,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:49.28,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,She probably took them off because \Nthey were hurting her feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:51.43,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,She had a band-aid on her heel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:55.03,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,Even bad guys have to deal \Nwith ill-fitting shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.03,0:12:01.32,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,But normally I wouldn't expect someone \Nto wear ill-fitting shoes to a drug deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:06.35,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible during the deal \Nsomeone might report them,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:09.47,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,and they'll have to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:13.87,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Ill-fitting high heels are \Nthe worst choice of footwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:19.72,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, her hair looks like she \Njust got it done at a salon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.72,0:12:21.17,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's not her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:22.69,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:25.68,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying evil women can't dress up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:29.23,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The guy's trading partner is \Nwaiting for a drug dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:33.31,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Normally you'd expect him to come wearing \Nsomething plain and inconspicuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:35.06,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,He actually was dressed that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:38.85,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It would be a different story if they \Nwere meeting in a deserted alleyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:42.00,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,but the deal is happening \Non the crowded Ebisubashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:46.35,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,If a badly mismatched couple met there,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:49.62,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,they would stand out in the \Nmemories of passers-by.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:54.33,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, the corsage on her \Nbag doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:57.15,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,If their meeting sign is a white rose,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.15,0:12:59.63,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,her corsage would be the same color.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:04.21,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,She wouldn't be confusing by \Nusing a differently colored rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:05.51,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:10.69,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Her elaborate hairstyle, ill-fitting \Nshoes, and rose corsage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:16.86,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The girl was probably invited to a \Nwedding or some other kind of party
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:15.02,DCMain,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:19.52,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,and is meeting her friend here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:21.13,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,He's right again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:23.31,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:24.59,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:26.28,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,That was all me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:27.53,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:31.79,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,That means the flashy guy talking to Kazuha
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:35.44,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,is the drug dealer's trading partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:40.29,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:42.03,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:44.86,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,but you'd be stupid to hit \Non a girl before a drug deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:47.30,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you assume he's hitting on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:52.31,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible Kazuha-chan spoke to him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.93,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's definitely not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:14:03.14,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Why would Kazuha talk to such \Na gaudy looking drug dealer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:05.94,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible they know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:10.23,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's also possible their deal was canceled,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.23,0:14:13.85,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,and he's just an ordinary person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.03,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Hattori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.03,0:14:21.00,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Normally you'd notice \Nthese things immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:23.87,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Though I do understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.52,0:14:27.76,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,It's one minute past the meeting time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:28.93,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:33.95,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,The dealer may already be at the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:35.93,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori, we're out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:40.09,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuha-chan could get caught up in \Nsomething if the dealer arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:42.78,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,You need to take her and get \Nout of there immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:44.44,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:47.20,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The video chat stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:49.38,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm emailing Kazuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:51.99,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking her who the flashy guy is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:54.60,DCMain,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break, Kazuha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:57.68,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,No way. You're not getting away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:15:00.34,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:03.75,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Heiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:07.01,Message,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Received Message
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:07.01,Doing,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:07.01,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He wants to know what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:14.01,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What is he doing with his jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:17.78,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The bulge under his arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:19.02,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,That must be
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:21.99,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:34.53,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What is he doing with his jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:37.71,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The bulge under his arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:39.54,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,That must be
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:42.83,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:44.79,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:48.60,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:50.34,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,That flashy guy's
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:53.19,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,hiding a gun on his chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.19,0:15:54.34,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:58.60,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Whether or not he's the \Ndealer's trading partner,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:16:01.57,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,he's definitely not just an ordinary citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:05.02,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori, forget about the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:08.87,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,You need to take Kazuha by the \Nhand and get away from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.87,0:16:10.94,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:12.99,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,She's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:15.05,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:18.16,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I just got a response from Kazuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:28.17,Message2,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Received Message
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:24.48,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,"I saw my old neighbor \NYakumaru-san at Ebisubashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:28.17,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was in his university's \Npharmaceutical department,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:31.33,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,but he's dressed so flashy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:33.17,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:37.50,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hanging around to see \Nwhat his date looks like."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:39.68,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What a stupid message!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.12,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,He's lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:47.11,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,A pharmaceutical student with bleached \Nhair, a neck tattoo, and pierced nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:48.31,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:52.44,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,He probably pretended to be a serious \Nperson and approached Kazuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:57.00,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuha's dad is the Osaka police chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:17:01.87,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's trying to butter her up so \Nhe can get information on the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:02.95,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:06.96,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:08.88,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kazuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:12.34,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Hattori! That flashy guy might be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:15.26,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you listening, Hattori?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:16.22,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:17.68,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:19.68,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're touching, moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:21.48,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:24.43,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?! Where are you taking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:27.08,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kazuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:29.02,DCItalic,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Heiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:34.65,DCMain,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:41.62,DCMain,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:44.12,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I could ask you the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:49.33,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing to my Kazuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:51.84,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Heiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.12,0:17:52.84,DCMain,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:58.13,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you brought a bunch of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:01.98,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,A whole bunch of ugly friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:03.01,DCMain,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:04.85,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:08.60,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll throw the lot of you \Ninto the Dotonbori River!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:10.23,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:14.26,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hattori!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:18.30,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,He hung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:24.66,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:29.17,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,That gaudy man was a narcotics agent?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.47,0:18:30.77,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:34.41,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,They investigate drug-related crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.41,0:18:37.72,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,They're called narcs or drug agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:40.59,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't that a kind of policeman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:43.56,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,You said he wasn't a cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:47.73,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Narcotics agents aren't police officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:48.23,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:50.89,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,They're agents of the Ministry of Health.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:54.23,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Because they're legally allowed to\Nconduct undercover operations,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:58.24,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,their agents can bleach their hair \Nor get tattoos and nose piercings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:03.37,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally they're allowed to have \Nguns if their jobs require it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:05.79,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.23,0:19:12.25,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard a lot of narcs are \Nformer pharmaceutical students.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:15.13,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's when it hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:19.30,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Then that man was there to \Nconduct an investigation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:20.69,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:24.40,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,According to the call I just \Ngot from Inspector Otaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:30.41,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,a drug dealer apprehended in Osaka\Nconfessed the location and sign of his deal,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:35.94,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,so that agent dressed up as him and \Nwas waiting for the drug dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.21,0:19:37.43,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:42.45,DCMain,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he asked his colleagues \Nto take her away from the location.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:43.38,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:46.50,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,If the dealer showed up, he \Nwould have found it suspicious,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:49.08,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,and he didn't want to get her involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:54.87,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like they caught the \Ndealer at a nearby comic café,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:57.01,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,so that settles that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:19:59.96,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,But is your master all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:06.69,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Once Inspector Otaki explained \Nthe situation, they let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.69,0:20:10.88,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,That's the least of his worries, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.43,0:21:41.27,Ministry,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Ministry of Health Kinki \NPublic Welfare Station
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.43,0:21:41.27,Ministry,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,General Affairs\NDivision\NHealth and\NWelfare\NDepartment\NNarcotics\NDepartment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.16,0:21:44.32,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Damn narcs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.85,0:21:47.70,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe they went \Nhard on a high school kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:50.20,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,They could've held back some.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.77,0:21:52.33,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:21:55.78,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, I got a huge lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.78,0:21:57.33,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Heiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.60,0:22:02.22,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,They'll talk to my dad for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.22,0:22:04.34,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.99,0:22:07.72,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Heiji. What did that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:08.34,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.62,0:22:12.98,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,When did I become yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.38,0:22:16.85,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.78,0:22:24.88,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,You said, "What do you think \Nyou're doing to my dear Kazuha?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.88,0:22:26.65,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll kill you, damn it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.08,0:22:31.53,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I-I didn't say anything that stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.34,0:22:35.13,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,I may not have gotten it quite right,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.13,0:22:37.55,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,but it was something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:41.29,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Heiji. Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.82,0:22:43.81,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Heiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.81,0:22:46.80,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Do I have to tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.11,0:22:49.35,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Heiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.06,0:22:54.01,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only going to say it once, so listen closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.50,0:22:58.03,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The most important thing to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.50,0:23:03.61,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,...is evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.94,0:23:04.98,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.79,0:23:09.50,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say weird things if you don't \Nhave the evidence to back it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.50,0:23:11.99,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, Heiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.99,0:23:13.47,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.47,0:23:15.95,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,I know what I heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.95,0:23:18.24,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there's something\Nwrong with your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.24,0:23:20.76,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,My darling, darling Kazuha-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:22.53,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.53,0:23:24.03,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,So you do remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.03,0:23:24.98,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:27.17,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,My ears are ringing so much, I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.17,0:23:29.01,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Heiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:31.00,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.00,0:23:33.20,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I'll email Ran-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.20,0:23:35.21,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.05,0:23:39.55,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I recorded it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.04,0:23:42.85,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing to my Kazuha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.98,0:24:09.00,DCEpPreview,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.93,0:23:50.99,DCMain,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Teams Detective Boys and Café \NRenno, please get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.02,0:23:53.21,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,It's our turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.21,0:23:54.37,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.12,0:23:56.59,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.59,0:23:58.37,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,He fell into the Teimuzu River!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.70,0:24:00.79,DCMain,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good! He can't swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.23,0:24:04.29,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,No. There's still something we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.06,0:24:09.00,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,We'll listen in on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.00,0:24:15.01,DCNextEp,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Teimuzu River Kite Flying Case\N(Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.78,0:24:14.56,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The next episode of Conan is "Teimuzu \NRiver Kite Flying Case, Part 1!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.94,0:24:35.03,Phone,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Phone
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.55,0:24:32.97,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.97,0:24:34.52,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.03,0:24:36.37,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're listening to it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.03,0:24:40.07,Don'tMiss,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.37,0:24:37.96,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's apparently his master's weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.96,0:24:39.85,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This is too funny. One more time.
